close_reason: Default project scope UX implemented and verified; linked-resource examples and dogfood no longer require redundant scope=project.
body: "User request 2026-05-17: remove the need to manually type scope=project in commands/options where the PM path already identifies the project context. Project scope should be the default for project-local operations. Global scope should remain opt-in for global pm package operations only. This should reduce token use and CLI friction for agents while preserving backwards compatibility."
